\subsection{Handling of \code{NA} values}{

Every indicator always emits \strong{leading \code{NA}s} for the initial
lookback period - positions where there is not yet enough data to
produce a result. This is separate from how \code{NA}s already present
in the input are handled, which is controlled by the \code{na.bridge}
